title: Kim Kardashian 'nervous and stressed' ahead of flying to Dubai after terrifying Paris robbery
text:
Kim Kardashian 'nervous and stressed' ahead of flying to Dubai after terrifying Paris robbery The star, who was robbed of millions worth of jewellery in October, made her first public appearance Share Kim kardashian (Photo: Splash News) Share Get daily updates directly to your inbox + Subscribe Could not subscribe, try again later Invalid Email 
Kim Kardashian West was "nervous" about her Dubai trip. 
The Keeping Up With The Kardashians star travelled to the city in the United Arab Emirates with Scott Disick for her first official engagement since she was robbed at gunpoint in Paris last October and the trip has gone "great". 
A source said: "Her Dubai trip has been great. Itâ€™s a work trip, but she has been sightseeing a bit as well. Kim Kardashian (Photo: Splash News) 
"She was nervous before she left, but says it was the right decision. She misses her kids, but had a great weekend. She was excited to spend time with her fans." 
And the 36-year-old television personality - who has North, three, and Saint, 13 months, with her husband Kanye West - was very "stressed" in the lead up to the trip but enjoyed herself when she got there. https://www.instagram.com/p/BPVo-v-juxR/?taken-by=kimkardashian&hl=en/embed 
An insider added: "She was stressed in the days leading up to leaving, but once she was there, she had an awesome time." 
Kim is also "very relieved" that the French police have made some arrests in regards to the robbery but she just wants to move on now. 
The source told People magazine: "She is very relieved the police is making progress. It was just pretty bad timing though, since she was already very nervous about the Dubai trip. https://www.instagram.com/p/BPVrAymjFR5/?taken-by=kimkardashian&hl=en/embed 
"Kim was very emotional before the trip and part of it was because she started thinking about the robbery. She is getting sick of having to relive that awful night and just wants to move on." 
The brunette beauty has been sharing pictures and videos of her trip on her social media account over the past few days. Her coverage began with a photograph of her and Scott on their way to Dubai. Like us on Facebook
